    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pins worn on the chest usually to hold a neck-cloth or scarf in place. Of varied design and materials but often decorative.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
